reviewText: I have owned several disks love the story but the disk I purchased from you is inoperable.  Please send another and verify it is usable prior to shipment.  Open it and play it.

Anyone who wants to make a difference in the world should see this documentary.  It will inspire you to share your own talents and love of life to help others in need.  This would motivate any church or civic group to find new ways of giving making community service fun and joyful.
